# after-hours-loop (optional rule)

When the user runs **`/after-hours`**, **`/after-hours-loop`**, or **`/loop`** with after-hours / overnight AFK instructions, load and follow:

`.agents/skills/after-hours-loop/SKILL.md`

Do **not** treat this rule as a standing overnight mandate. The loop only runs when the user (or an explicit Cursor Automation) invokes it. Stop phrases: `stop after-hours`, `stop loop`, `/after-hours stop`.
